000&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Contact batyspestcontrol\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/90 to-brand-900/70\"></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><nav class=\"text-sm mb-6\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><li><a class=\"text-surface-400 hover:text-accent-500 transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><span class=\"text-surface-600 mx-2\">/</span></li><li><span class=\"text-accent-500 font-medium\">Contact Us</span></li></ol></nav><span class=\"inline-block bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded mb-6 shadow-md\">Get In Touch</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white leading-tight\">Contact batyspestcontrol</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-surface-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">Have questions or need a quote? We&#x27;re here to help with all your pest control needs across the nation.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"inline-flex items-center bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-accent-600 transition shadow-xl\"><span class=\"mr-3 text-xl\">📞</span>614-926-0787</a><a href=\"mailto:info@batyspestcontrol.com\" class=\"inline-flex items-center bg-white text-brand-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-surface-100 transition shadow-lg\"><span class=\"mr-3 text-xl\">✉️</span>Email Us</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white border-b border-surface-200 py-6\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-between items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-surface-600\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 text-2xl mr-3\">⏱️</span><span class=\"font-bold tracking-wide\">24/7 Emergency Service</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-surface-600\"><span class=\"text-emerald-500 text-2xl mr-3\">🛡️</span><span class=\"font-bold tracking-wide\">100% Satisfaction Guaranteed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-surface-600\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 text-2xl mr-3\">💲</span><span class=\"font-bold tracking-wide\">Free Estimates</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-accent-500/10 text-brand-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4\">Contact Information</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6 leading-tight\">Let&#x27;s Connect</h2><p class=\"text-surface-600 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium\">Whether you&#x27;re looking for a quote, have questions about our pest control services, or need immediate assistance, our team is ready to help.</p><div class=\"space-y-5 mb-10\"><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"flex items-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group border border-surface-100\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-5 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-inner\"><span class=\"text-brand-900 text-2xl\">📞</span></div><div><span class=\"block text-surface-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Phone</span><span class=\"text-brand-900 font-black text-xl group-hover:text-brand-600 transition\">614-926-0787</span></div></a><a href=\"mailto:info@batyspestcontrol.com\" class=\"flex items-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group border border-surface-100\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-5 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-inner\"><span class=\"text-brand-900 text-2xl\">✉️</span></div><div><span class=\"block text-surface-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Email</span><span class=\"text-brand-900 font-black text-lg group-hover:text-brand-600 transition\">info@batyspestcontrol.com</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-start p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-surface-100\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-5 flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner\"><span class=\"text-brand-900 text-2xl\">📍</span></div><div><span class=\"block text-surface-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Service Area</span><address class=\"text-brand-900 font-bold text-lg not-italic leading-relaxed\">Nationwide Coverage<br/>USA</address></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-brand-900 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 text-2xl\">⏱️</span>Business Hours</h3><div class=\"space-y-4 text-surface-300\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-brand-800\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Monday - Friday</span><span class=\"font-bold text-white\">8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-brand-800\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Saturday</span><span class=\"font-bold text-white\">9:00 AM - 4:00 PM</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-brand-800\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Sunday</span><span class=\"font-bold text-white\">Emergency Only</span></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-brand-800 flex items-center bg-brand-800/50 -mx-4 -mb-4 p-4 rounded-b-xl\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 text-2xl mr-3\">⚡</span><span class=\"text-accent-500 font-extrabold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm\">24/7 Emergency Service</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl border border-surface-100\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3\">Send Us a Message</h3><p class=\"text-surface-600 mb-8 font-medium text-lg\">Fill out the form below and we&#x27;ll get back to you as soon as possible.</p><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Your Name <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"John Smith\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-surface-200 focus:border-accent-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none transition shadow-sm font-medium text-brand-900 placeholder-surface-400\" name=\"name\"/></div><div><label for=\"phone\" class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Phone Number</label><input type=\"tel\" id=\"phone\" placeholder=\"(555) 123-4567\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-surface-200 focus:border-accent-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none transition shadow-sm font-medium text-brand-900 placeholder-surface-400\" name=\"phone\"/></div></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Email Address <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-surface-200 focus:border-accent-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none transition shadow-sm font-medium text-brand-900 placeholder-surface-400\" name=\"email\"/></div><div><label for=\"service\" class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Service Needed</label><select id=\"service\" name=\"service\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-surface-200 focus:border-accent-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none transition shadow-sm font-medium text-brand-900 appearance-none\"><option value=\"\">Select a service...</option><option value=\"termite\">Termite Treatment</option><option value=\"rodent\">Rodent Control</option><option value=\"bedbug\">Bed Bug Treatment</option><option value=\"ant\">Ant &amp; Roach Control</option><option value=\"mosquito\">Mosquito Control</option><option value=\"other\">Other / Not Sure</option></select></div><div><label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Message <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-surface-200 focus:border-accent-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none transition shadow-sm font-medium text-brand-900 placeholder-surface-400 resize-none\"></textarea></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-brand-900 font-black text-lg py-5 px-8 rounded-xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 mt-4\">Send Message</button><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-surface-500 font-medium mt-4\">We respect your privacy. No spam ever.</p></form></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-[#0a1128] text-white pt-24 pb-20 md:pb-12 border-t border-brand-800 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-5\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative flex items-cent